Day 5 of 30 Skincare Myths with Ash! 
Let’s put some hold to these skin crimes. 

🚫 Myth: Popping pimples helps them go away faster.
✅ Fact: Popping is never the first choice — it spreads bacteria, causes inflammation, and leads to more breakouts (and even scars).

Instead, treat acne smartly:
✨ Use ingredients like Kojic Acid, Niacinamide, and Retinol for regular breakouts.
🔥 For cystic acne, a touch of Benzoyl Peroxide can help calm it down — without the damage.
💧Always pair treatments with a gentle anti-bacterial face wash and soothing acne cream.

Let’s stop the pop and start healing the right way. Your skin will thank you! 💆‍♀️🌿
